DDTSIZE   LLLLLLLLLLLLUUUUUUUUUUUU CCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCC
----------------------------------------------------------------
DDTSIZE
Type: Adverb   (String*8)
Use:  An Adverb which controls type of DDT test executed when
      running DDTEXEC and DDTLOAD.  Three possible values are
      SMALL, MEDIUM and LARGE.
     'SMALL'  256x256 image, 2000 clean components, 8000 vis
     'MEDIUM' 512x512 image, 5000 clean components, 15000 vis
     'LARGE'  1024x1024 image, 15000 clean components, 75000 vis
----------------------------------------------------------------
